                    <span>Rather than discuss the technical aspects of this book...<P>Through using the LAB Profile, I've become a better salesperson, businessman, friend, and father.<P>I thought I was a good communicator and influencer before reading this; this book saved me years of learning by my own experiences.</span>
                  
              
